info.hasDepFromThisWallet: Check whether the payment method of the withdrawal request matches the payment method of the deposit. If the details match at least one used method, the command is True.
info.documentsVerified: Check if the Identity toggle switch in the user profile is active.
info.paymentSystemVerified: The number of payment methods (cards) that have been verified and have an active toggle switch.
info.phoneVerified: Check if the Phone toggle switch in the user profile is active.
info.emailVerified: Check if the email is verified via the Email toggle in the user's profile.
info.unprofitGamer7Days:
Checking¬†the IN - OUT of the user for the last 7 days:

If negative, the outcome is True,
if positive or equal to 0, it is False.
info.isMultiacc: True ‚Äî if the user has unblocked multiple accounts.
info.hasPayoutsOnReview: True - If the user has at least one request on review.
info.isFirstPayout: True - If this is the user's first payout, unsuccessful requests are not counted.
info.isAutoPaymentEnabled: Check if automatic payout is enabled in the user's profile.
info.isPotentialCrossCurrencyTypePayout: It is set to true if there were deposits in fiat money and an attempt to withdraw to crypto or vice versa. Deposits for the last 30 days are checked. There is a certain specificity while the list of fiat and crypto methods is configured by the hard code. When adding a new method for payments, you need to add it to the corresponding list through a development task. Example: 'inpay','interac','pix','paydo'.
info.verifiedWalletsCount: The number of confirmed payment methods in the user's profile whereby the deposit was made.
info.suspended: The user account has been temporarily suspended, check the restriction details.
info.trustedWalletsCount: The number of payment methods (wallets) that do not require verification. It is configured using methods in AntiFraud-Payments Methods.
info.walletsCount: The number of payment methods in the user's profile whereby the deposit was made.
info.transactionSum: The amount of the current transaction in the account currency.
info.transactionSumUsd: The amount of the current transaction in USD is converted at the current exchange rate.
info.waitingTransactionSum: The amount of transactions in the waiting status (confirmed by the financial manager but have not received the final status from the payment system) in the account currency.
info.waitingTransactionSumUsd: The amount of transactions in the waiting status (confirmed by the financial manager but have not received the final status from the payment system) in USD.
info.currentHour: The current hour, according to the LR UTC admin panel.
info.botAlreadyPayedPerTime: Number of withdrawal requests paid by bot per period $range - number of withdrawal requests paid by bot per period $range
info.payedToday: The sum of successful clients' withdrawals (OUT) + the sum of withdrawals in the Waiting status made for the current day from 00:00 to 00:00 of the next day according to the admin panel time.
info.payedThisWeek: The sum of successful clients' withdrawals (OUT) + the sum of withdrawals in the Waiting status for the current calendar week from Monday to Sunday.
info.payedThisMonth: The sum of successful client withdrawals (OUT)¬†+ the sum of withdrawals in the Waiting status for the current calendar month.
info.playerDailyLimit: The daily withdrawal limit set in the client's profile.
info.playerWeeklyLimit: The weekly withdrawal limit set in the client's profile.
info.playerMonthlyLimit: The monthly withdrawal limit set in the client's profile.
info.cohortDailyLimit: The daily limit, according to the withdrawal cohort, set in the Cohort Settings.
info.cohortWeeklyLimit: The weekly limit, according to the withdrawal cohort, set in the Cohort Settings.
info.cohortMonthlyLimit: The monthly limit, according to the withdrawal cohort, set in the Cohort Settings.
info.LTIN: The amount of successful deposits (IN) made by the client for Life Time stated in the account currency. When calculating, conversion from USD is performed. Therefore, due to exchange rate movements, there may be inaccuracies in the calculation. This is not a bug and is accepted as an allowed deviation.
info.LTOUT: The amount of successful withdrawals (OUT) made by the client for Life Time stated in the account currency. When calculating, conversion from USD is performed. Therefore, due to exchange rate movements, there may be inaccuracies in the calculation. This is not a bug and is accepted as an allowed deviation.
info.LTINUsd: The sum of the client's successful deposits (IN) for Life Time in USD.
info.LTOUTUsd: The sum of the client's successful withdrawals (OUT) for Life Time in USD.
info.winback: The value of a user's winback.
info.initialWinback: The value of the user's winback before the last deposit was made.
info.cohortId: ID number of the cohort the user is in.
info.usedNoDepGiftsPerTime: Function with an additional parameter "a number of days". It gives the number of no-deposit gifts used by the client for the last 72 hours.
info.vipStatus: The client's segmentation status is entered in vip status field of the Profile
info.firstDepSumUsd: The amount of the client's first deposit stated in USD.
info.successDepositsCount: The number of successful client deposits for Life Time.
info.successPayoutsCount: Number of successful withdrawals per client Life Time.
info.country: Country of registration of the player.
info.paymentMethodType: The type of payment method from Marbella settings. CARD, ONLINE BANKING, CRYPTO, VOUCHERS, WALLET.
